column5: Will be headed for the kawarthas for a week in about a week, what is the price of gas at the marinas? In the past they were 10 cents per litre more than at the gas station. So about $1.12?
our marina is 1.25/litre fill the jerry cans before you leave home!
About $1.30 on sturgeon, and supposedly our marina is the chapest on the lake right now!  Bring gas for sure!!  Sinker
